    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies Metalink, an XML-based download description format.  Metalink describes download locations (mirrors), cryptographic hashes, and other information.  Clients can transparently use this information to reliably transfer files. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
